defaultPromote
default Britain’s standing and reputation in the US to build our influence across the country.
default&#xa0;
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStrengthen the bilateral defence relationship;
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultMaintain close collaboration with US security authorities to reduce the threat to the UK from terrorism, organised crime, and cyber attacks;
